{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2131112, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "想知道他会得到什么代价，dz能和我们分享一下嘛(*^_^*)", "timestamp": 1627196372, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2131115, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz作为朋友，无法忽视他对他人的帮助、共情和友好。不该因为他的错误否定他的一切。", "timestamp": 1627196392, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2131117, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": 2131112, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 如果思考一下他虚荣、造假的目的，就能理解他最看重的已经被击碎了。", "timestamp": 1627196450, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2131118, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是的，没必要编造谣言和人身攻击", "timestamp": 1627196454, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2131122, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "#政治相关", "timestamp": 1627196500, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2131123, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "分手、说自己年级前三拿过一二九奖学金、作弊...你管这叫“一件亏心事”？", "timestamp": 1627196519, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2131129, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": 2131123, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 的确是因为假装没有分手这一亏心事，引起的所有人在这个主题下对他的错误也好、看法也好的讨论。", "timestamp": 1627196580, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2131137, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": 2131117, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 啊这…dz是说他太痴情了所以现在是对他的惩罚？？", "timestamp": 1627196677, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2131139, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "他具体有啥优点吗？麻烦dz分享一下，完全没觉得有", "timestamp": 1627196713, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2131148, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": 2131137, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不是...比如说他人设崩塌、虚荣的幻想破碎、和人相处的心理压力", "timestamp": 1627196798, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2131164, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": 2131148, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 举个例子dz，假设他作弊，除了人设崩塌之外他还应该受到学校的处罚；已知他男女德行有亏，为什么除了人设崩塌之外不能有外界舆论谴责呢？", "timestamp": 1627197071, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2131165, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": 2131148, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主:差不多得了😅", "timestamp": 1627197113, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2131167, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": 2131164, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 当然，这是他应得的。子弹已经飞了很久，当事人应该已经看到了，作为朋友只是担心他的心理问题。", "timestamp": 1627197181, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2131186, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": 2131167, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你人是挺好的，但是看起来他干这些事之前怎么没想过自己会不会有心理问题呢", "timestamp": 1627197416, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2134595, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哪有什么代价呀，很多不看树洞的同学还蒙在鼓里帮他说话呢，无语了", "timestamp": 1627235006, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2135926, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413342, "reply_to": 2134595, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: ...在朋友圈公开为他说话吗", "timestamp": 1627274925, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 10, "pid": 413342, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "认识他很久，他的确有虚荣、自以为是、不够真诚的缺点，也了解他为了获取资源采取的功利手段。这个事情他的确错了，很多事情他也的确做错了。但是他也得到并会得到他应得的代价，任何人都不希望自己因为一项亏心事而激发为黑而黑的山呼海应和舆论狂欢。人非圣贤孰能无过，作为朋友，羞愤他的行径，却也害怕抹杀他的信心和希望。期待他改过吧。", "timestamp": 1627196283, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1627274925, "url": "", "vote": {}}}